      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ZIPPING KRAVITZ (8) is a sprinter who excels over the short dashes. Finished third latest over 457m at Q Lakeside (25.37) in a Grade 4 but is better suited here over less ground. Has never missed the frame here at the trip from seven starts. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card last start despite being beaten. Leading chance again. SECRET STORY (7) has a strong record here with 17 wins and seven placings from 25 starts. Was out of placings last time (25.62) at Q Lakeside in a Grade 4, finishing fourth and beaten 8 lengths. Can hit the frame with the right run. RUPESH (4) has a strong record this track and trip including seven wins from nine starts. Below best last time at this track (19.90) in a Free For All, finishing a 1.4 lengths fourth. Looks one of the chances. CASINO SPECIAL (1) is worth a look over a shorter distance this time.",
